# Cloud Run images build from the repo root (so the Dockerfile can install the shared/ +
# pipelines/ packages). Include only what an image needs; exclude everything else — notably the
# gitignored cross-repo symlinks (model-gpr, hazard_analysis, Learning, damage_modeling, …), which
# point at absolute paths outside the repo and would break the build context, plus data/, .venv/, .git/.
*
!shared
!pipelines
!scripts
!cloudrun
